My_video_game: Secure Economy & Fair Play
My_video_game is an ambitious project focused on a high-fidelity "Treasure & Currency" economy. We bridge the gap between skill-based rewards and sustainable game balance while prioritizing developer privacy and safety.
🛡️ Privacy & Security First
We are committed to Privacy by Design. To protect our contributors:
• Location Privacy: We never store or track the physical whereabouts of our team.
• Sensitive Data: All local configs, IP addresses, and API keys are strictly excluded via .gitignore.
• Anonymous Collaboration: All financial and contribution tracking is conducted via secure GitHub handles.
💰 Economic Mission: The "Faucet-Sink" Model
To combat poverty loops and hyper-inflation, our economy follows a strict ratio-based system:
• The Faucet (Rewards): Treasure is earned through skill, ensuring every player has a fair start.
• The Sink (Costs): Repairs and tiered upgrades maintain currency value.
• Majority Stack Tax: To ensure no single player dominates the market, top earners contribute to a "Newcomer Pool," ensuring a sustainable ecosystem for everyone.
🚀 Contributor Quick Start
1. Secure Your Environment: Ensure your .gitignore is active before pushing code.
2. Review Rules: Read CONTRIBUTING.md for our economic guidelines.
3. Use Templates:
• [PAYOUT]: Submit all revenue-sharing requests here.
• [AUDIT]: Report on "Win vs. Spend" ratios to help us balance the economy.
• [SECURITY]: Report any potential data leaks immediately.
4. Communicate: Use GitHub handles only. Never share personal banking details in public threads.
⚖️ Roadmap
• Phase 1: Economy Stability (Faucets vs. Sinks).
• Phase 2: Majority Stack Redistribution.
• Phase 3: Secure League Liquidity Integration.
